\id JAS JAS: KHARAM Bible Translation 1st Edition 
\h James 
\toc1 JAMES Chemajia 
\toc2 James 
\toc3 Jam 
\mt1 JAMES 
\mt2 Chemajia 
\imt1 Chonglamsaat 
\ip \bk James larik hi \bk* James inti miring inkhat in imajia eii. Hiwa James hi Jisu naipa kha lei-ete tia inngaidon. James hi koisuok karoon alei-eii halli Jerusalem uparup karoon um alei-eii (Chuon 15:13). Tirton Paul in James hi koisuok karoon “Kachou” tia Galatia 2:9 khan aril. Kasing kathei ngai'n James larik hi Jisu inneisuo thengnga kum soomra-nga pheiwei khan James imajia eii tia inngamna. James hi Jerusalem koisuok karoon ejarra hiwa larik hi Jerusalemma omlai khan imajia lei-ete tia inlei. 
\ip James in hiwa larik hi inchekchaiya kaom Israel zaat soomleini ngaidiang imajia eii (1:1). James imajia larik hi christian rakip in juisik-ah arei eii takkha “Zaat soomleini” tia amajiana ajarchu hiwa larik hi Jihudi christian ngaidiangtak ileimajia eii. Hiwa larik hi rahooi katamtak diang imajia ejarra, chongmun katamtak um aril. James in ngamna li chuon jarra, akadik ngamna khan chuon le inruoisik eii jarra (2:17), Inchong mi ngaidiang mimeel mimai enmaknasik jarra chongthakna anei (2:1-4), halli katha-ah ngaidonli chonghi rilsik jarra einidiang aril (3:1-12). 
\iot Asuungnga kaom Chong 
\io1 1. James in ama chemajia akateel mi ngaikha minpaakna anei \ior (1:1)\ior* 
\io1 2. James in christian ngaidiang poongraal nakhan kadei karaat eru tia masokna anei \ior (1:2-27)\ior* 
\io1 3. James in ngamna kha chuonna malarro tijarra majiana anei \ior (2:1-26)\ior* 
\io1 4. Chong hi angtuk ranak kaneime tijarra aril \ior (3:1-12)\ior* 
\io1 5. James in Pathian lungsing lungwar hi manmasituol lungsing lungwar khale in-angmak tijarra rilna anei \ior (3:13–4:10)\ior* 
\io1 6. James in in-or emaru tijarra chongthakna anei \ior (4:11–5:6)\ior* 
\io1 7. James in jetsik kasuok minchu mindikna ngaikha majia ah minhekna anei \ior (5:5-20)\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Pathian khat-um Pumi Jisu Christa suok ka-eii James kei'n: 
\p Manmasituol pumpuiya inchekchaiya kaom Pathian mi ngai rakip kha khoya thona kanei. \rq Matt 13:55; Mk 6:3; Chuon 15:13; Gal 1:19\rq* 
\s1 Ngamna li Lungsing Lungwar 
\p  
\v 2 Ulenai ngai, poongna raalna angjet ning-intongpui phakhan rokna phakha min-eru,  
\v 3 ajarchu poongna raalna kha nangni ngamna khan amator li kadei karaat ning esik eii tikha nangni'n ningjet.  
\v 4 huui katungnga kachang khat-um iteii insam kaboi ning enasik, kadei karaat khan kapur omlekleiya naruoirase.  
\v 5 Nangni tu ka-ang in lungsing lungwar ning-insam inchu, nangni diang nakapesik Pathian amadiang nirasu; ajarchu Pathian in minpaam kaboiya khat-um minriangnga mi rakipdiang apeii.  
\v 6 Takkha nangni'n ningni phakhan, in-ngamsam omlekleiya ngamnaru, ajarchu in-ngamsam kanei ama khachu thiraang in ruoinarei iruoi tuipui tuiphuksaan ka-ang eii  
\v 7 Khawa miring khan Pumi diangnga inphut iteii inkhat-um kamusik eii tia ngaidon marase;  
\v 8 khawa miring kha achuon thona rakip-ah malung inthuul intheek halli malung kangir matormak miring kha eii. 
\s1 Sara li Inchong 
\p  
\v 9 Sara ka eii Christian ngaikha Pathian in kadomsaang phakhan inroksik eii, 
\p  
\v 10 halli inchong Christian ngaikha Pathian in nuoi minnung phakhan inroksik suok. Ajarchu inchong itihi reipar kachuoi angnga alachuoisik eii. 
\p  
\v 11 Kani khan satheiya jo-eella halli reikuung kha ajuochar; aparkha ajuota halli apar katha kha ajuochuoi. Hiwa angnga inchong hi-um inmani inchongna chuonkhan inmangsik eii. \rq Isa 40:6,7\rq* 
\s1 Matheemna khat-um Poongna 
\p  
\v 12 Poongraal kadei inmani ngaikha rawaan katha eii, ajarchu inmani'n poongraal kha indeisuoli mai in-ar phakhan, inmani'n Pathian in ama kaminriang ngai sik-ah ida ringna lukhu kha intumsik eii.  
\v 13 Hiwa ka-ang poongraal khan namatheem phakhan, “Hiwa matheemnahi Pathian diangnga inphut kajuo eii,” eini'n timui ajarchu Pathian kha kathamak in matheem matormak, halli ama apumtak innum tuteii matheemmak.  
\v 14 Takkha eini taksa imanuom kathamak khan namator phakhan einidiang matheemna aheiwa.  
\v 15 Taksa imanuom kathamak hong-injir phakhan manu aheichoi, halli manu khan pui hongphali thina aheichoi. 
\p  
\v 16 Ulenai ngai, maleisei khan intormaru.  
\v 17 Kutchoi katha khat-um puikatung kutchoi rakip hi marwaan makheiya kajuo eii; raliim angnga inthuul kaboi marwaan na kaom war ngai kabool, Pathain diangnga inphut kajuo kha eii.  
\v 18 Ama lungdou dungjuiya achong kadik khan eini naminjir jei, khawa khachu ama kutbool rakip karra mansakhet-ah hong-inra kha ni-enasik eii. 
\s1 Karangai khat-um Katho 
\p  
\v 19 Ulenai ngai! hiwahi ngaidonru, miring rakip inngai innot eru, takkha karil insuum li karaang insuum kha eru.  
\v 20 Manmasi raangna khan Pathian dikna kha mintungmak.  
\v 21 Khawa jarra akachok nunchan khat-um akathamak rakip mathaantru. Pathian diang inpeluutru halli nangni sanminringna kanape mator ningmalungnga nathunpi chongkha keiluutru. 
\p  
\v 22 Ama chong ningrangai khan ningtheinuo ah maleisei inthomaru; khawa rathuulla chuonna thoru.  
\v 23 Tu inkhat in chongkha inrangaili chuonna inthomak inchu, meengsialla ameel in-en miring ka-ang kha in-eii.  
\v 24 Ama'n ameel kha katha-ah in-enli asi halli innottheiya ameel kha ang changme tikha amanil.  
\v 25 Takkha mi ngai lungdouwa kamasuo puikatung dan khan in-en halli karangaibit emak-ah katha-ah manil omlekleiya chuonna intho inchu inchuon thona rakip ah Pathian in rawaan apesik eii. 
\p  
\v 26 Nangni karra tume biaklam kacheet-ah kajui tia kangaidon? Namalei kha nasur matormak inchu, na-ijui biaklam kha nemna kaboi eii halli natheinuo ah maleisei katho kha na-eii.  
\v 27 Pa Pathian in inthiang khat-um biaklam iti khachu hi eii: nuli pa kaboi ngaili chuulmei ngai inpoong inraal kaalla kasan halli manmasituol kathamak in intormak hi eii. 
\c 2  
\s1 Mimeel Mimai enjarra Chongthak 
\p  
\v 1 Ulenai ngai, akalur Pumi, eini Pumi Jisu Christa diang kangamna ngai ning-ejei keengnga, nangni'n mimeel mimai enli mi karathial kha emaru.  
\v 2 Mi inchong inkhat soonna kutsabi li puondiar katha inluk-ah nangni inchunnakhan aheiwa, halli puonchet puonwai inluk-ah sara ka eii miring inkhat-um aheiwa tia leirui.  
\v 3 Nangni'n puondiar katha-ah inluk miringpa khadiang khoya ningthowiaiya, “In-ongna kahoikhet hin in-ongro,” amadiang ningti takkha sara miring padiang chu, “Sosun ngirro, emakli kakeii kuungnga neipilla in-ongro” ningti inchu,  
\v 4 nangni'n ningsuunga inkhoithen ningbool halli akathamak malungnga chong ningtan jarra nangni dikmakchu. 
\p  
\v 5 Rangairu, ulenai ngai! Hiwa manmasituolla sara miring ngaihi ngamna-ah inchong halli ama kaminriang ngaisik-ah idapi ama chong-inkhitna Rengram kha kamusik-ah Pathian in akadang.  
\v 6 Takkha nangni'n sara ngaikha khoya thomakchujei! Nangni kanaminpoong ngaikha inchongngai emuwabe? Inchongngai emuwabe chongkatan ngaidiang nangni nakeitoot-ah kanaruoi?  
\v 7 Nangni ramingroon katha karilse ngaikha inmani emuwabe? 
\p  
\v 8 Pathian chong-inthiang khan nimu, “Indiang inwaipui ngaikha napumtak niminriang angnga minriangro,” iti Rengram dan kha ningjui inchu, akatuun kha nangni'n ningthojei. \rq Levi 19:18\rq* 
\p  
\v 9 Takkha mimeel ning-enli mi khoya ningtho inchu, nangni manu katho ning eii, halli Dan kha'n nangni kha dankamakoi ngai ning-eii ati.  
\v 10 Chongpeii inkhat kamakoi ama khan chongpeii rakip kamakoi kha eii. 
\p  
\v 11 “Zool-inthai thomaro,” kati ama khan, “Mikathat emaro,” kha-um ati. Nangni'n zool-inthai ningthomak innum, mikathat ning-e inchu Dan kamakoi kha ning ejei. \rq Suok 20:13,14; Innidan 5:17,18\rq* 
\p  
\v 12 Nilungdouwa kanamasuo dan kha'n chong atansik mi ngai ang-inlang rilru khat-um thoru,  
\v 13 ajarchu Pathian in chong atanpha khan minriang kajetmak miring kha minriangnuni, takkha minriang khan chongtan kha amator. 
\s1 Ngamna li Chuon 
\p  
\v 14 Ulenai ngai, miring inkhat in ngamna kanei tili chuonna amalar mak-inle, ang athana omme? Khawa ngamna khan ama sanmator nibo?  
\v 15 Puondiar khat-um baksik kaneimak ulenai inom tia leirui.  
\v 16 Halli nangni'n inmani diang ningti, “Pathian in rawaan naperase! kalumma omru halli kakhop-ah bakru!” nangni'n inmani diang arei ka-ekha ningpemak inle, ang athana omme?  
\v 17 Khawa angnga: ngamna kha chuon inchelmak inchu, akathi kha eii. 
\p  
\v 18 Takkha miring inkhat in tite, “Miring inkhat in ngamna anei, leiilaak miring in chuon anei.” Takkha kei'n kati, “Nang ngamna kha chuon inchel lekleiya naminmuro, halli kei ngamna kha chuonle inruoiya naminmu kate.”  
\v 19 Pathian inkhatbit eii tihi nangni ning-ngamnabo? Thajei! raikhuo ngai-um khawa kha ingamna halli inchile inruoiya intuul.  
\v 20 Ka-am miringngai, chuon inchelmak ngamna kha nemna kaboi eii tihi nangni'n ningmuzootbe?\f + \fr 2:20. \fq nemna kaboi \ft manuscript lekkhat achu hintia injia \fqa kathi.\f* 
\p  
\v 21 Nipa Abraham in asapa Isaac kha maichaam pena munna chuonle inruoiya ape jarra akadik miring tia inlei emak abe? \rq Inphut 22:1-4\rq* 
\p  
\v 22 Nangni'n ningmu khachu ama ngamna li chuon kha inruoiya insi, halli ama ngamna kha achuontho khan ajar-eya huui mintung. 
\p  
\v 23 Halli hintia chong inthiangnga lei-injia Pathian chongkha huui hongtung, “Abraham in Pathian ngamna, halli ama ngamna khan ajar-eya Pathian in akadik miring tia alei,” halli Abraham hi Pathian sappui tia akoi. \rq Inphut 15:6; 2 Khang 20:7; Isa 41:8\rq* 
\p  
\v 24 Nangni'n ningmu khachu eini ngamna khabit-in emak takkha nichuontho khan einihi Pathian diang akadik mikha ni-eii. 
\p  
\v 25 Hile in-ang rip-ah zool-inthai Rahab kha-um ama'n Israel ruongngai ngaikha akeiluut khat-um lamleiitiang aminsiya inringkhuo sanna chuon atho jarra Pathian diang akadik mikha a-eii. \rq Jam 2:1-21\rq* 
\p  
\v 26 Ratha inchelmak taksa kha akathi angnga, chuon inchelmak ngamna kha akathi eii. 
\c 3  
\s1 Malei 
\p  
\v 1 Ulenai ngai, akatam khatchu ocha hong-emaru, ajarchu nangni'n ningjet, khachu ocha ka-eii eini ngaihi kheeldoomma chong anatansik eii.  
\v 2 Eini rakip insuina ninei, achongrilna rakip-ah insuina kaneimak miring inom inchu, ama kha puikatung miring eii halli apum rakip kha insur mator.  
\v 3 Sakor hi eini iti juinasik-ah abaiya thirrui nithun, halli eini minsinazoot reiya niminsi mator.  
\v 4 Rakuong hi minkhina khat-ah leirui, Thipui kangar ominnum, akalok Rakuong kha akasep pa'n akasiin rakuongsung inliing na-ah aminsinazoot reiya aminsi.  
\v 5 Hile in-ang rip-ah, malei hi pumma kaom akasiinthei saram inkhat eii takkha loktheiya in-or mator. 
\p Ngaidonru, akasiin meicheii inkhat in akalok ramchangkhat akaangwiak mator!  
\v 6 Malei hi mei ka-ang eii. Nipumma kaom kadikmak khet saram inkhat kha eii, nipum rakip aminchok, meikhur makheiya kahong mei kha'n niringkhuo pumpui meiya aminkaang.  
\v 7 Manmasi eini'n ramsa, wa, awonna intoot khouring, khat-um nga inti khouring rakip ngaihi nisur mator,  
\v 8 takkha tu miring innun malei hichu surmatormu. Malei hi surmator kaommak akathamak kha eii, thinasik tur in kasip eii. 
\p  
\v 9 Malei ya eini'n Nipumi khat-um Pa Pathian kha niminpaak; halli Pathian ramilla ibool mi ngaidiang um khomaak nisaamna. \rq Inphut 1:26\rq* 
\p  
\v 10 In-angrip mur makheiya minpaakna khat-um khomaak saamna kha asuok, ulenai ngai, hiwahi akadik emak!  
\v 11 Tuiring inkhat makheiya akathum li akakha tui suoksuom niabe?  
\v 12 Ulenai ngai, theichang kuungkhan ruongmoot kara abe, emakli theibom kuungkhan theichang kara abe? karamak, aka-al tuiring kha'n tuikathum suokmak. 
\s1 Pathian diangnga inphut Lungsing lungwar 
\p  
\v 13 Tume nangni karra akasing khat-um jetmatorna kanei? aringkhuo omchan katha khan ama'n malarrase, lungsing lungwar khat-um nunchan inchuolna chuonkatha itho khan malarrase.  
\v 14 Takkha namalungnga kara-ot, ka-ngep, khat-um phaamrai kase na-e inchu, nang lungsing lungwar khan in-or inlang akadik chungnga manu thomaro.  
\v 15 Khawa lungsing lungwar kha marwaan makheiya kajuo emak; manmasituol takha eii, ratha lamtiang emak khat-um raikhuo makheiya eii.  
\v 16 Kara-ot khat-um phaamrai kase omna munkhan, inthiarmak khat-um kathamak rakip omsik eii.  
\v 17 Takkha marwaan makheiya kajuo lungsing lungwar khachu mansakhet-ah inthiang; kadai, nunchan inchuol, malung inthiang, inriang kasip, akatha chuonkatho, mimeel mimai ka-enmak khat-um malungtak karoon hi eii.  
\v 18 Akadai kabool mi ngaikhan akadai muchi kha inwor halli akadik kha inrakhool. 
\c 4  
\s1 Manmasituol le Sap ka-eii 
\p  
\v 1 Nangni karra insuol khat-um inseii ngaihi huwa makheiya kaheiwame? nangni suungnga inchatleiya raal nanthopui taksa inmanuom hoina makheiya kaheiwa eii.  
\v 2 Nangni'n phur ningmanuom, takkha nangni'n neimakchu, khawa jarra nangni mikathat sik-ah ning-insuuk; nangni'n phur khat ningmanuomhek, takkha nangni'n neimator makchu, khawa jarra nangni'n ning-insuol khat-um ning-inseii. Nangni'n ningmanuom kha neimakchu ajarchu nangni'n khawa sik-ah Pathian diang nimakchu.  
\v 3 Halli nangni'n ningni phakhan, nangni'n changmakchu, ajarchu ningngaidon kha thamak; nangni taksa hoinasik lamtiang inliingnasik phur ngaikha ningni.  
\v 4 Nangni zool-inthai mi ngai! manmasituol le sap ka-e hi Pathian le inhal eii tihi nangni'n jetmakchube? Manmasituol le sap ning-ezoot inchu, nangni ningpum tak-in Pathian le inhal ningbool eii.  
\v 5 “Eini diang Pathian in inapeii ratha khachu kara-ot in asip” tia Pathian chong-inthiang khan injia kha lailam eii tia ningleibe? 
\p  
\v 6 Takkha Pathian riangwai kha kheella anapeii. Pathian chong-inthiang khan ati, “Pathian in in-or miringkha zootmak, takkha nunchan inchuol miringdiang riangwai apeii.” \rq Chongil 3:34\rq* 
\p  
\v 7 Khawa jarra, ningpumtak Pathian diang peru. Seitan kha zootmaru, halli nangni diangnga inphut ama'n ataansik eii.  
\v 8 Pathian koolla heiwaru halli ama'n nangni koolla aheiwasik eii. Ningkut ngaikha rasuru, nangni manu karoonngai! Ningmalung ngaikha minthiangru, nangni a-omchanbit katho-ngai!  
\v 9 Kapoong kha eru, chapru, halli inwairu; nangni innuina kha chapna khan inthuulrase, halli nangni hoina kha kaziing khan inthuulrase!  
\v 10 Pumi maikuungnga nunchan inchuolru, halli ama'n nangni naminsaang sik eii. 
\s1 Miringkhat chungnga chong tanmaknasik Chongthak 
\p  
\v 11 Ulenai ngai, nangni li nangni inrilthai maru. Nangni'n Christian miringkhat kha ningrilthai emakli chong ningtan inchu, nangni Dan kha ningrilthai khat-um chong ningtan kha eii. Nangni'n Dan kha chong ningtan inchu, nangni Dan kajui ngaikha emakchujei, takkha Dan chungnga chongkatan kha ning ejei.  
\v 12 Pathian bit-eii Dan kanapeii halli chong katansik. Ama bit-in nasan khat-um naminmang mator. Miringkhat chungnga chong katan sik-ah nangni tu kin-eii ning-intime? 
\s1 In-or Chungnga Chongthak 
\p  
\v 13 “Wini emakli ziingnga eini'n khuopui angjet-ah sinita, eini'n kumkhat omnita halli sial lounita sialyam nimahuumsik eii” kati nangni, tuun keidiang nara-ngairu. 
\p  
\v 14 Nangni ringkhuo hi ziingnga ang esikme tihi jetmakchu! Nangni hapkhatliai sik-ah inlarliya kamangrit ziingkhum ka-ang kha ning-eii. \rq Chongil 27:1\rq* 
\p  
\v 15 Hiwa hi-eii nangni'n ningtisik kasuok: “Pumi lungdou e-inchu, eini'n ringrui halli hiwa emakli khawa kha thorui.”  
\v 16 Takkha tuunchu nangni'n ning-in-or, ninglok-or; khawa in-orna rakip ngaikha dikmak. 
\p  
\v 17 Thosik-ah akatha eii tia nijetli eini'n nithomak inchu, khawa kha manu eii. 
\c 5  
\s1 Inchong diang Chongthak 
\p  
\v 1 Tuun inchong mi ngai, keidiang nara-ngairu! nangni chungnga kaheiwasik poongna jarra chapru khat-um inwai inlang chapru! 
\p  
\v 2 Nangni inchongkha mangjei, halli nangni puondiar ngaikha in-ngeii'n bakjei. 
\p  
\v 3 Nangni soonna li dangka kha thir-eek kanjei, halli hiwa thir-eek in nangni chungnga sakhi eta halli nangni taksa kha mei angta akaangsik eii. Nangni'n ahekna nikhuo ngaihin ningkarei ngaikha ningbuk. \rq Matt 6:19\rq* 
\p  
\v 4 Nangni ningleiya chuonkatho ngai chuonthoman kha eteii pemakchu. Inmani ngai chaprasa kha ra-ngairu! Nangni leiya chuonkatho ngai chaprasa kha Pathian, Akaraatkhet Pumi kuorkuung tungjei. \rq Innidan 24:14-15\rq* 
\p  
\v 5 Hiwa nuoipilchung ringkhuo hin nangni taksa hoina li inchong karaang ringkhuo-ah ningomjei. Thina nikhuo sik-ah nangni'n ningpum katha-ah ningwaijei.  
\v 6 Nangni'n kamasialmak akadik mikha noonkuung ningpeya ningthat, halli ama'n nangnidiang zootmak thomak. 
\s1 Kadei Karaat khat-um Pathian diang Kani 
\p  
\v 7 Ulenai ngai, kadeiraat eru, Pumi juomaklaiseng. Enru leimi ngai'n in-iwor muchi ngaikha akatha hong-inra sik eii tia ka-ngaaklan omlekleiya inngaak. Inmani'n ka-ngaaklan omlekleiya khuolum khat-um suunlai ruosur kha in-ngaak.  
\v 8 Nangni um ka-ngaaklan emaru. Nangni ngamna kha mincheetru, ajarchu Pumi ajuonasik nikhuo kha anaijei. 
\p  
\v 9 Ulenai ngai, Pathian in nangni chungnga chong tanmak nasik nangni li nangni inzootmak thomaru, ajarchu chong katanpa kha inkhar kuungnga ngirra omjei.  
\v 10 Ulenai ngai, poongraal na-ah ka-ngaaklanmak ngai minkhina sik-ah, Pumi ramingnga kaleiril Pathian Chongkachoi ngaikha ngaidonru.  
\v 11 Rawaan katha mi ngai tia eini'n nikoi ajarchu inmani kadei inraat. Nangni'n Job deiraatna thurchi kha ningjetjei, halli ahekna achu Pumi'n amadiang ipeii ngaikha nangni'n ningjetjei. Pumi chu minriang khat-um minriang malungroon in asip. \rq Job 1:21,22; 2:10; Minpkla 103:8\rq* 
\p  
\v 12 Ulenai ngai, marwaan emakli nuoipil emakli ang-khattak raming ti-inlang chongkhomaak insaammaru. Nangni'n ningzoot kha kinzoot tiru ningzootmak kha zootmung tiru, khawa e-inchu Pathian chongtanna nuoiya omnutun. \rq Matt 5:34-37\rq* 
\p  
\v 13 Nangni karra tume kapoong? Inmani'n Pathian diang nirasu. Nangni karra tume karok? Inmani'n minpaakna laa sakrasu. 
\p  
\v 14 Nangni karra tume kana? Inmani'n koisuok uparup ngai koirasu, achungnga olive sariak minnootrasu halli Pumi ramingnga Pathian diang minnirasu. \rq Mk 6:13\rq* 
\p  
\v 15 Halli kangamnale inruoiya Pathian diang innipi khan kanapa kha adamsik eii; Pumi'n inpumma kana kha mindamsik eii halli inmani'n manu inleitho ngaikha ngaidam pisik eii.  
\v 16 Nangni'n ningdam nasik-ah, ningmanu ngaikha inrilsuokru halli inkhatli inkhat sik-ah Pathian diang innipiru. Akadik miring in Pathian ini khan ranak om khat-um akatha aheichoi. 
\p  
\v 17 Elijah eini ka-ang miring inkhat alei-eii. Ama'n ruo surmaknasik Pathian diang malung kaluut-ah aleini, halli kumthum le tharuk hi neipil chungnga ruo leisurmak. \rq 1 Reng 17:1\rq* 
\p  
\v 18 Ama'n Pathian diang aleininook, halli marwaan makheiya ruo ajuosur khat-um neipilchung khan angrakip hong-inra jei. \rq 1 Reng 18:42-45\rq* 
\p  
\v 19 Ulenai ngai, nangni karra miring inkhat akadik makheiya lamleiitiang aleisiya halli miring inkhat in ahongruoikir inchu,  
\v 20 Akadikmak lamma leikasi kha woikhat akadik lamma akahongruoikir miring khan khawa miringpa ratha kha kathisik-ah inphut asan halli manu katamtak kha amakhupi tihi ngaidonru.